<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"/>
		<meta name="keywords" content="한국에너지재단" >
		<meta name="description" content="한국에너지재단">
		<title>mail</title>
	</head>

	<body style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">
	<div style="width: 590px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px 30px; text-align: center; border-top: 15px solid #02468a;">
		<div style="overflow: hidden; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 20px 0; text-align: left;">
			<h1 style="float: left; display: inline-block; padding: 0 0 0 2px; margin: 0; font-size: 25px; letter-spacing: -0.04em; font-family: 'Malgun Gothic', 'Malgun Gothic', '맑은고딕', '돋움', 'Dotum';">
				<img src="${server_domain}/images/front/common/logo_color.png" alt="한국에너지재단"/>
			</h1>
			<strong style="float: right; padding: 30px 0 0 0px; font-family: 'Malgun Gothic', 'Malgun Gothic', '맑은고딕', '돋움', 'Dotum'; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #333333; letter-spacing: -0.04em;">
				발신일 : ${mailSendDate}
			</strong>
		</div>
		<div style="overflow: hidden; margin: 0; text-align: left;">
			<div style="overflow: hidden; margin: 0 0 30px 0; padding: 30px; border: 20px solid #f3f3f1; background: url('${server_domain}/images/front/mail/mail_bg.png') no-repeat 440px center;">
				<p style="font-family: 'Malgun Gothic', 'Malgun Gothic', '맑은고딕', '돋움', 'Dotum'; font-size: 26px; font-weight: bold; color: #000000; letter-spacing: -0.08em;">
					<span style="color:#02468a;">${title}</span>
				</p>
			</div>
			<div style="overflow: hidden; padding: 0 20px;">
				<p style="margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: 'Malgun Gothic', 'Malgun Gothic', '맑은고딕', '돋움', 'Dotum'; font-size: 16px; font-weight: normal; color: #333333;">${content}</p>
			</div>
			<div style="margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center;">
				<button style="display: inline-block; width: 255px; height: 50px; line-height: 50px; border: 0px; cursor:pointer; background-color: #0a69c8;" title="홈페이지 바로가기">
					<span style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; font-family: 'Malgun Gothic', 'Malgun Gothic', '맑은고딕', '돋움', 'Dotum'; ">
						<a href="${server_domain}>홈페이지 바로가기</a>
					</span>
				</button>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div style="overflow: hidden; padding: 0 20px; margin-bottom: 100px; border-top: 2px solid #d7d7d7; text-align: left;">
			<p style="overflow: hidden; padding: 20px 0 0 0; margin: 0; font-family: 'Malgun Gothic', 'Malgun Gothic', '맑은고딕', '돋움', 'Dotum'; font-size: 14px; color: #333333; letter-spacing: -0.05em">
				본 메일은 발신 전용 메일로써, 한국에너지재단 홈페이지의 이메일 마케팅 수신 동의 여부에 관계없이 운영상 고객공지 목적으로 발송되었습니다.	
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	</body>
</html>
